title: Joe Bonamassa - Live Bootleg Collection - SBD or FM Quality
description:
Hello All --

Been on a HUGE Joe Bonamassa kick lately, so I thought I'd take time to share a "best of" collection of the live shows I've been cranking at unthinkable volume.

Each of these is FM or SBD sourced, high-quality MP3 320 or V0, correctly track-listed, tagged with correct show artwork and iTunes ready.  

Hey, if something's worth doing, it's worth doing right.

Joe B.'s playing on these is OUTRIGHT SICK.  Fans will go nuts over this stuff, folks that have never heard of him will become instant fans.


FZW Dortmund (2006)
BBC Maida Vale Studios (2008)
BBC Maida Vale Studios (2-17-10)
Lightning 100 FM Nashville (2002)
Live at Rockpalast 
Live at WMSE Studios (2004)
Schwarzer Adler, Germany FM (2005)
Shepherds Bush Empire, London (2007)
WXPN World Cafe, Philidelphia (2009)

ENJOY my friends!  As always, PLAY LOUD!
